field.name: CREATE_EVENT_TABLE
field.value: "CREATE TABLE events (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, event_id INTEGER, start_time INTEGER, end_time INTEGER, planned_amount_of_drinks INTEGER, with_who INTEGER, start_time_answer INTEGER, end_time_answer INTEGER, day_time_answer INTEGER, comment TEXT, event_checked INTEGER, timestamp INTEGER);"

field.name: CREATE_GOAL_TABLE
field.value: "CREATE TABLE goals (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, start_time INTEGER, end_time INTEGER, length_in_days INTEGER, goal_id INTEGER, amount INTEGER, complete INTEGER, timestamp INTEGER);"
